# 2. React Component Rules

## 2.1 Always use functional components
No class components, ever.

## 2.2 Component structure order

Components MUST follow this order:

1. Imports  
2. Types/interfaces  
3. Component function  
4. Hooks (state, effect, memo, callback)  
5. Internal helpers  
6. Return JSX  
7. Export  

Example:

```tsx
import styles from './Card.module.scss';
import { useMemo } from 'react';

export interface CardProps {
  title: string;
  children?: React.ReactNode;
}

export const Card = ({ title, children }: CardProps) => {
  const hasContent = useMemo(() => !!children, [children]);

  return (
    <div className={styles.card}>
      <h3 className={styles.title}>{title}</h3>
      {hasContent && <div className={styles.body}>{children}</div>}
    </div>
  );
};

